sheSystem.name: sheSystem

revisions.description: Add managed objects as to TimeZone
IUS Release 2. Correct access for sheSystemControlExternalTime.
Change Description for sheSystemVersion.
Change the description for the possible values of sheSystemVersion string.
Take over by Gerd Barchmann for R2.5.
Correct description for some sheSystemConfigLogFtp - parameters. Username and password could never be readout via snmp if. Correct spelling of variables in sheSystemSwmControl.
Correct some names and definitions for backward compatibility. Add ControlReqResult and ControlReqStatus to sheSystemConfigLogControl. Correct SheSystemDnsServerNameControlRequestType.
Add group sheSystemAutoConfigBackup for backward compatibility. Will not be supported by R2.5.
Add new system-version string.
Add new system-version string for R2.5.2. Add new tables for configuration of IP host and static routes via snmp.
Expand sheSystemFileControlTypeOfFile for alarmLog and uptimeLog.
Modify SheSystemIpHostTable after late review comment.
Modify sheSystemIpHostTable and change ..Usage attribute to ..Description.
Remove index limits for IpHost- and IpRoute-table.
Replace system-version string R2.5.2 with R2.6.
Modify unit and range for sheSystemNtpClientXmitInterval and sheSystemNtpClientControlXmitInterval.
Add new system version R2.7 and R2.8.
Add new system version hiX5622/R1.0. Modify comment for sheSystemIpHostUseDhcp.
Add systemversion string for R3.0.
Add metric parameter to interface route table (CO hiX13598).
Correct missing Object list for swm externalFtpAccessAlarm.
Expand valid range for TimeZone configuration.
Add new system version string for R2.6S2, R2.7M and R2.8M.
Modify valid values for Timezone configuration.
Support new file request type for upload of all available inventory records.
Add new system versions for feature specific versions of R2.7M.
Add systemSwmCurrentStatus with changed and alarm trap.
Add new sytem versions represented by new shelftypes. Modify enum definition for SheSystemSwmCurrentStatusType.
Update systemversion information.
New parameter in sheSystemIpHostTable for .1p confoguration of the used vlan's.

sheSystemControlRequest.name: sheSystemControlRequest
sheSystemControlRequest.description: System commands : configureTime : The command to configure the external time. tmnConnect : the command for a manager to connect in order to be allowed to manage the SHE and to stop the NE sending the sheSystemStartupEnd trap. tmnDisconnect: the command for a TMN to disconnect from the NE. lctConnect : the command for a manager to connect as a LCT. The SHE then sends the sheSystemLctSession trap. lctDisconnect: the command for a LCT to disconnect from the NE. The SHE then sends the sheSystemLctSession trap. If a LCT does not disconnect a LCT session is automatically disconnected by the SHE after a internal timer expired. writeDatatoFlash: the command to start writing configuration data of all subsystems to flash-memory (long running command). configureTimeZone: the command to change the current timezone. setCPUThreshold: the command to configure the threshold that when CPU usage exceeds the certain limit, notification is sent. setMemoryThreshold: the command to configure the threshold that when Memory usage exceeds the certain limit, notification is sent. Notifications : sheSystemStartupEnd, sheSystemLctSession, sheSystemWriteDatatoFlashFinished, sheSystemChangedCPULoadThreshold, sheSystemChangedMemoryThreshold.

sheSystemFileControlRequest.name: sheSystemFileControlRequest
sheSystemFileControlRequest.description: File management commands : upload : a file is uploaded to the FTP server from the SHE NE. download : a file is downloaded from a FTP server to the SHE NE. uploadCardsAllOfType : upload for all cards af the same type. downloadCardsAllOfType : download for all cards af the same type. uploadAllOfSystem : Only for upload of all available remote inventory records! Parameters specify the type of file and the FTP server. downloads: - SW to a singleCard : commands to load a new load - SW to all cards of a type - restoreFile (configuration files) uploads: - log files - restoreFile (congfiguration files) - remote inventory (also AllOfSystem) - performance data Notifications : sheSystemFtp sheSystemSwLoadPromoted Alarms: sheSystemSwmFtpAccessError sheSystemSwmFtpExternalAccessError

sheSystemDbmControlRequest.name: sheSystemDbmControlRequest
sheSystemDbmControlRequest.description: Database Management commands : setSystemMaintenanceBase: - Set needed ftp access information for automatic DB request's. notifications: sheSystemDbmBaseSet backupDb : - The command for a manual database backup into the FEPROM of the DSLAM and to the FTP server. The return value commExecStarted indicates the beginning of DB storage. notification: sheSystemDbmResult refreshDbBackupFilesTable : - The DSLAM supports several backup files. The command retrieves the backup files at the FTP server and provides their file names and time and date of creation in the table sheSystemDbBackFilesTable. notification: sheSystemRefreshDbmBackupFilesTable dbReloadSpecificFile: - Reload a specific file from sheSystemDbBackFilesTable into the DSLAM. If successful, the CXU perform a reset for activation. notification: sheSystemDbmResult setBackupPeriod: - Configure the backup period settings for automatic remote backup to ftp server and local backup to EEPROM. notification: sheSystemDbmBackupPeriodSet setLocalBackupAdminState: - Enables or disables the automatic local backup feature. notification: sheSystemDbmLocalBackupAdminstateSet setRemoteBackupAdminState: - Enables or disables the automatic remote backup feature. notification: sheSystemDbmRemoteBackupAdminstateSet
